&lt;p&gt;In our reality, people from diverse races, nationalities, and backgrounds come together to enjoy important cinematic works of creativity, intellectual expansion, identity, and equality. In this world, there are no boundaries around people because they are embraced by a universal understanding of humanity. This is the element of commonality that weaves through this annual event of images from Africa, the African Diaspora, and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
